#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Independent D3-S3 crossrow oracle — constructible BLOB vectors (stdlib only).

Does NOT import/invoke production C. Append-only on frozen d3s2 144-prefix.

Usage:
  generate [out.json]              # default path: spec/vectors/domain-scan-crossrow-v1.json
  check [in.json]                  # default path: same; rebuild-equality gate
  emit-c-fixture <in.json> <out.h> # required args; usage+exit 2 if missing
  self-test                        # deterministic oracle + RED mutation suite

REP1 micro-units: W (walk, no exact_get) / G (exact_get burst, row_budget=0) /
WG (BIND only: walk + eligible gets). SELECT phase2/sem0 is pure W; companion
setup for Mode27 / Mode29 APPLICATION_FIRST is SELECT_SETUP G at phase2/sem6.
"""
